  m_text: "\tWelcome, stranger! Your task is to collect some amount of yellow glowing
    crystals. But beware: this territory is populated with dangerous axe-wielding
    zombies. So, do not forget to restore your health and recharge your batteries
    at the base before exploring the map. Remember: to collect crystal you have to
    bring it to the collection point near the factory. You can only haul one crystal
    at a time."
